fields.physical_description: Design: cards printed with an illustration on one side and mottled blue on the reverse; some illustrations are drawings, others photographs
fields.title: memory game; original memory.  made under licence from otto maier verlag
fields.history_note: lid is printed to show photographs of the cards and a family scene playing the game.
fields.historical_context_note:
Rewards: winning pairs
Forfeits: n/a
No. of Players: two or more
Equipment required: cards
strip of yellow card printed in black with the letters a to i and k
strip of yellow card printed in black with the numbers 1 to 10

Rules:
The aim is to match the pairs of cards and the winner keeps the pair; the winner is the one with the greatest number of pairs.
